Package: nvtop
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libc6 (>= 2.34), libncurses6 (>= 6), libncursesw6 (>= 6), libsystemd0 (>= 240), libtinfo6 (>= 6)
Recommends: systemd
Description: NVTOP stands for Neat Videocard TOP, a (h)top like task monitor for GPUs and accelerators. It can handle multiple GPUs and print information about them in a htop-familiar way.
